The.Originals.S03E02.1080p.HDTV.X264-DIMENSION
Aired 15.10.2015

"You Hung the Moon"

After discovering that poachers have begun
taking out werewolves in the bayou, Elijah and
Jackson grow concerned for Hayley's safety
when she fails to show up during the full
moon. Meanwhile, Davina, the only one with the
answer to Hayley's whereabouts, plots ways to
use that to her advantage. Elsewhere, Cami
approaches Klaus with her theory on who is
behind the series of murders in the French
Quarter, while Lucien delivers to Elijah an
unsettling warning about the war brewing among
the sire lines. Finally, after receiving a
dire prophecy about the future of the
Mikaelson siblings, Klaus takes extreme
measures to determine the validity of this
potential impending threat.

17/Slower
Evolve... or die.
